STAT

Stat (object) will reveal information about an object provided such an object
is currently in the game.  (name, type, worn, flags, affects, etc.)

Stat (player, mob) will reveal information about that creature provided it
is currently in game.  (name, location, alignment, level, xp, etc.)

Stat room will reveal information about the room you are in.  (exits, 
description, keys required)

You may prefix (object, player, mob) by x.  where x is the number of the
creature you desire to stat.  Hence, stat 123.sword gives information on
the 123rd sword from where sword.

